ref=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報67.29美元一桶，升2.08美元或3.19%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,296.4美元一盎司，升102美元或1.97%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報65,590.06美元，跌1,785.61美元或2.65%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報3.962厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國勞工統計局周五公布，1月份生產者價格指數(PPI)上漲0.5%，高於0.3%的預測，比上月多出0.1個百分點。 剔除波動較大的食品和能源價格的核心PPI經季節調整後上升0.8%，高於12月份的0.6%增幅，遠超預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">企業消息方面，該串流媒體巨頭<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Netflix;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NFLX/\">Netflix</a>放棄收購 Warner Bros. Discovery 的計劃，此舉令 Paramount Skydance 成功達成對該荷里活片廠的收購。雖然收購失敗，但市場認為是好事，股價收市升逾13%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國抵押貸款融資公司Market Financial Solutions(MFS)進入破產程序，市場擔心MFS倒閉，可能會對銀行股造成損失，多間銀行股受壓。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:富瑞;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JEF/\">富瑞</a>(JEF.US)跌高達9.3%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MS/\">摩根士丹利</a>(MS.US)挫6.2%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美銀;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BAC/\">美銀</a>(BAC.US)、巴克萊銀行(BCS.US)跌約4%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:富國銀行;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/WFC/\">富國銀行</a>(WFC.US)跌5.6%，拖累道指今日大跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OpenAI周五宣布完成1,100億美元融資，未計入本輪集資資金估值達7,300億美元。 公司表示，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>於本輪融資中投資500億美元；軟銀及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">英偉達</a>(NVDA.US)則各投資300億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息指，SpaceX考慮最快3月保密提交IPO文件。這家由億萬富豪馬斯克創立的火箭和衛星公司，正推進史上最大規模的上市計畫，有望在6月掛牌上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:16;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:巴郡;cpos:16;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BRK-B/\">巴郡</a>新行政總裁 Greg Abel 預計將於周六發表其接替 Warren Buffett 後的首封年度致股東信，並將與該集團的季度及 2025 年業務更新一併公布。</p></div>",
